captions.text: Normally you hit the kicker five times trying to get a trick done, and then your knees and back start to hurt whenever you hit the flat water.
With this kind of landing you can try a lot of new things, and I hope this will proceed in the next few years.
In the finals I had a hard crash onto my back, but it didn't hurt at all. I had fallen down and didn't notice anything, I just slipped into the water and everything was fine.
